{"tid":518252,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"番工第十一日就唔知醒","createTime":"2018-01-03T06:32:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-05T03:14:05.000Z","uid":42759,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f53ee79ccc9c95585d118395167117da9cfbea72","tid":518252,"uid":42759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T06:32:40.000Z","msg":"講一講我背景先，我係一個九十後黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁早排轉左新工，做侍應。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n琴晚收尾番屋企又掛住打機，四點先訓。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以今日兩點先起身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n本身番十二點！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第一時間即刻打比老闆say sorry啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：我      <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：老闆<br />\n<br />\n我：老闆我今日病左呀（係佢未講野果陣我已經爭住講）<br />\n<br />\n之後佢就收左綫。<br />\n<br />\n而家點算好，佢係咪炒硬我？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbf0e3b312ff2088c5ccad4467cda908f360177f","tid":518252,"uid":18366,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T06:33:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3e7d2b39bfd9a2c99a293035ad0cc4e7702e7777","tid":518252,"uid":42759,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"fbf0e3b312ff2088c5ccad4467cda908f360177f","tid":518252,"uid":18366,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T06:33:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T06:38:08.000Z","msg":"緊張打多左咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" cla